                    <lb n="1" style="text-direction:up-top-down"/><supplied reason="undefined" evidence="previouseditor"><persName><name nymRef="#?"><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ᚋᚐᚊ</supplied><unclear reason="damage">ᚔ</unclear>ᚋᚑᚍᚓᚇᚔᚐᚄ</name> <w type="formula" lemma="maqqas">ᚋᚐᚊᚔ</w> ᚋᚒᚔᚁᚔᚈᚔ</persName></supplied>
